  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0baf \u0b8f\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bcd  \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd 15 \u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Russian Aeroplot Airline Case: Court Decision on 15th",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Commercial High Court's decision on whether to dismiss the case filed against an aircraft owned by Russia's Aeroflot will be announced on the 15th.",
        "On behalf of the Airport and Civil Aviation Services Company named as the 2nd defendant in the said case, the case was called for hearing on June 28 and the Additional Solicitor General, President's Counsel Sumathi Dharmavardhana, submitted a request to dismiss the case on behalf of the Attorney General.",
        "Colombo Commercial High Court Judge Harsha Setunga, who investigated the issues, called this case as a special case for hearing on the 5th yesterday and announced that after examining the issues, he would issue an order whether to dismiss the petition or not.",
        "However, yesterday the case did not come up for hearing before Commercial High Court Judge Harsha Setunga. Instead, it was heard before Commercial High Court Judge Sumit Perera.",
        "The court announced that the case will be heard again on the 15th to decide whether to dismiss the case.",
        "The case was filed by Celestial Aviation Trading Limited in Ireland.",
        "Ireland-based Celestial Aviation Trading Limited has filed a complaint against Aeroflot Russian Airlines for failure to comply with the terms of the lease agreement between the two parties.",
        "In this case, in relation to this petition, lawyer Lasantha Hetty Arachi appeared on behalf of the Russian airline company and President's lawyer Avinra Rodrigo appeared on behalf of the petitioner Irish company Anura de Silva.",
        "It is noteworthy that a team including Senior Deputy Solicitor General Mahen Kopallava and Deputy Solicitor General Rajeev Gunathilaka are present on behalf of the Attorney General."
      ],
